r=#A62A2A>(1/21/02 2:52:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1138.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pstr-m05.ygpweb.aol.com/data/003/43/CD/1E/9E/JdD8sfYfp4xVsdHGsp9Dij1DL+JDYJ+c0180.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why we love FV</span><hr size=1> Not one to often voice my opinion in public forums, I thought I should do it here, not only to add my voice to the chorus of those that love this server, but also in case anyone from Verant happens by here.<br>
<br>
I love Firiona Vie.  This server is wonderful.<br>
<br>
1. Roleplay.  Only once, in the last year and a half of playing this game did I encounter any roleplay on the servers I tried before, Bristlebane and Tholuxe Paells.  Once.  I love to roleplay.  I have a character with a developed background and personality that defines how I act in game.  I strive to remain in character at all times, unless forced to OOC for important reasons or to help players with questions not answerable in character.  I have roleplayed more in just the last week than ever on another server.  Multiply that times the weeks since this server opened, and I am having a great time.<br>
<br>
2. Twinks.  I hate twinks.  I despise running by orc hill and seeing someone in 70k worth of equipment.  Not only because it is annoying to see someone in equipment that they did not earn (that character, I don't care if your alt earned it, you didn't.), but because it is unfair to other players without that advantage.  They create a feeling in lower level character, especially new players, that they are not as good since they don't have similar equipment.  Once they understand why, it creates feelings of resentment and jealousy.  But, primarily, I hate it because twinks, especially at low levels, don't group.  They take an entire area that should support a low level group and kill everything to power level themselves.  That is what really bothers me.  The 1 character limit and TLC combine to drastically reduce twinking.<br>
<br>
3. Languages.  Thank you, you actually managed to make languages interesting.  I like some other ideas that have popped up about making NPC's speak racial languages, but I'm happy to at least have this.  I spent 30 minutes in Ak'anon, gesturing and leading a gnome around when we did not share a common language to get him to help me turn Nitrates into the Zoo guy for the Regurgatonic.  It was so much fun in the end, when he got it, I was smiling and laughing out of game.  I also rewarded the young gnome with some platinum which I hope helped him on his own endeavors.<br>
<br>
There are other reasons I love this server, and if this discussion continues on, I might chime in again, but for now, I'd just like to say thanks to creators and players who gave this server its uniqueness and to everyone who even attempts to roleplay.  <br>
<br>
Faelyndrea Wintersdawning<br>
31st Circle Wizard of the Court of the Crosswinds <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=1138.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=1138.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1138.topic&index=26><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.threadControl?topicID=1138.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1138.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1138.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Day<option value="firionaviefrm23">Hero Heart Tavern<option value="firionaviefrm15">The Polling Booth<option value="firionaviefrm40">Kudos!<option value="firionaviefrm2">The Market Square<option value="firionaviefrm22">The Tradeskill Shop<option value="firionaviefrm38">T